#: ../../deployment/rknn.rst:5 b7c886904241443a8c7dd59f561d5326
msgid ""
"VoxCPM-RKNN2 deploys VoxCPM-0.5B on **Rockchip RK3588** edge devices using "
"the RKNN2/RKLLM NPU acceleration stack."
